# Pages (`src/pages/`)

- **Routing** is filesystem-based. Dynamic segments use `[...slug]` or `[tag]` as in this repo; paths pass `params` aligned with `entry.id` or tag strings from `posts` frontmatter.
- **Collection pages** should follow the existing pattern: `getCollection("<name>")`, map to `getStaticPaths`, `render(entry)`, wrap with the correct layout from `src/layouts/`, pass `frontmatter={entry.data}` where applicable.
- **Marketing/static pages** generally use `BaseLayout` directly (e.g. home, contact, pricing, `blog/tags/*`, `legal/about.astro`, `system/*`).
- **RSS** is `rss.xml.js`; item links must stay consistent with `blog/posts/[...slug].astro` (`/blog/posts/${entry.id}`).
